https://www.linkedin.com/in/wael-moawad-929b56112/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABxKZrEBjXmVMHszbgvL5diEuTwkIQPDQyY", "recommendations/1/context": "Aung Myo was senior to Kush but didn't manage Kush directly", "recommendations/1/date": "April 15, 2019", "recommendations/1/description": "It was great time working with Kush in IRD team of W Doha. Kush is creative and innovative. He never say no to his guests nor his team, he lives in the brand philosophy of “whatever/whenever and get it done, make it happen”. Kush is a very positive and an open minded person, and of course a great leader who lead by example to his team. ", "recommendations/1/name": "Kush Srivastava", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Assistant Director of Banquets & Outside Catering@ W Doha Hotel & Residences | Hospitality, Catering", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kush-srivastava-73415195/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABQh-9gBPonnh2rwTuXPlla63jJnb0x9BjE", "recommendations/2/context": "Aung Myo reported directly to Kirsten", "recommendations/2/date": "February 22, 2015", "recommendations/2/description": "I was very lucky to work with Kirsten in Raffles Salon at Raffles Dubai. 9 months was a very short period for me, I never think enough to learn from her. She consistently supports me to grow higher and never hesitate to empowered me or allow me to make my own decisions. She has a very positive attitude and always had fun at work. I had got a chance to learn her quality selling techniques that make the outlet kept busy with lots of reservations. I impressed with her strategies of team engagement that make us kept motivated, learn and grow. I wish to work with her again in future when the right opportunity comes. ", "recommendations/2/name": "Kirsten Williamson", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Hunter Valley Boutique Wine Sales", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kirsten-williamson-0b91191b/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQcSk0BLlq4axIwgLKy0uB_ltgPGIftQH0", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Alla worked with Aung Myo on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "June 28, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Accidentally our hospitality pathways got crossed with Aung at 1st Baku European Games. We where a parts of large task force team brought from all over the world. Aung impressed me with his professional approach, passion, dedication and “Out of box” mind set. He is great team player and accountable person. I would certainly recommend him to any employers he will speak in the future! ", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Alla Ovrakhova", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "🇺🇦 Proudly Ukrainian •Help desk associate 🧜🏻‍♀️ 🚢", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alla-ovrakhova-4a913682/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABF2CkEBfQsucZksuXVBJQyTkjPv3w0kPAg", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Kush reported directly to Aung Myo", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "April 15, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Aung is a very nice team player and he knows very well how to drive the team\nAn outstanding leader in all aspects\n", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Kush Srivastava", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Assistant Director of Banquets & Outside Catering@ W Doha Hotel & Residences | Hospitality, Catering", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kush-srivastava-73415195/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABQh-9gBPonnh2rwTuXPlla63jJnb0x9BjE", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Wael managed Aung Myo directly", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "March 2, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "I'm delighted to write this recommendation to whom concern, \n\nAung is one of the best I have ever seen or worked with,  He isn't looking to do his job or his task only but he's always go above and beyond to reach to the highest levels of excellence. \n\nAung is very talented in administration skills , handling team and easily to deal with diversity , very motivated players , able to build his team and create very enthusiastic work environment. \n\nAung is very valuable asset wherever he's , I'm very confident to write about him and if I will continue writing about him I will not stop.\n\nWael Amer\nFood and beverage manager \nSofitel Cairo El Gazira", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Wael Moawad", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Bachelor's degree at Fayoum University", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/wael-moawad-929b56112/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABxKZrEBjXmVMHszbgvL5diEuTwkIQPDQyY", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Kirsten managed Aung Myo directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "December 30, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Aung Myo Kyaw for 9 months in the Raffles Salon of Raffles Dubai. Aung consistently displayed high levels of dedication to his role of Supervisor. I was able to rely on him to run the outlet single-handedly on a regular basis. Aung is able to instill pride and cooperation within his team and always promotes a positive work attitude. He has an excellent eye for detail and is able to develop relationships with many guests on a regular basis. I feel fortunate to have had him as part of my team.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Kirsten Williamson", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Hunter Valley Boutique Wine Sales", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kirsten-williamson-0b91191b/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQcSk0BLlq4axIwgLKy0uB_ltgPGIftQH0", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Zaw worked with Aung Myo on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "June 10, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "It's my pleasure to recommend Aung as my previous colleague who work for Raffles Dubai as a Lobby Lounge Supervisor currently.( # 1 of 473 Hotels in Dubai for 2014 rank by TripAdvisor)\n\nAung is a good team player and able to lead his colleagues during operation hours also training side. He is  the one who use to bring the new idea to his department regarding training & presentation of outlet operation. Due to his outstanding ,motivation & knowledge, he reached two steps of promotion up to Food & Beverage Supervisor. He is a person who have  a high consistency of following company standards & procedures. As a team leader, customer & employee satisfaction are up to 100% under his supervision and operation were smooth as silk. \n\nAung's performance & hard working, I don't have any doubt for his career of hospitality & I wish him to get every success in his future endeavor.\n \nSincerely, \nZaw Win Tun \nCabin Crew, Qatar Airways", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Zaw Win Htun", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Cabin Crew at Qatar Airways", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/zaw-win-htun-2796487a/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABDTI30B0mVyUWqEqjhYBB2A0BTN07c8dXo", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Ahmad managed Aung Myo directly", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "April 19, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "I was very lucky to have Aung in team at Raffles Dubai, AUNG He's Very Talented, Motivated, Creative, Hard working, Great team player, Self started person with great attitude. He never say NO for any challenge always there whenever needed, I can see very bright future in front of him, I highly recommend him for any good employer, I wish him all the best in his career and i wish to work with him again in the future when the right opportunity come.", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Ahmad AlAdham", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "Director of Food & Beverage | Quality Assurance & Audits | Operational Excellence | Strate